{'relation': ['https://d-scholarship.pitt.edu/48493/', 'https://cesf.pitt.edu'], 'title': ['This is How we Do It: Lessons Learned from Three Branches of Community Engagement at Pitt'], 'creator': ['Sarode, Trupti', 'Gauvin, Nancy', 'Durham, Aliya', 'Caldwell, Keith'], 'description': ['This poster will explore the synergy between academic departments and institutional efforts toward meaningful change in communities.  \r\n\r\n\r\nDrawing on lessons from experiential learning, place-based initiatives, and examples of community engaged praxis in teaching and research in three academic units, this poster will highlight shared insights on ways to foster lasting partnerships for effective community engagement.'], 'date': ['2025-03-04'], 'type': ['Conference or Workshop Item', 'NonPeerReviewed'], 'format': ['image/png'], 'language': ['en'], 'rights': [None], 'identifier': ['https://d-scholarship.pitt.edu/48493/1/Gauvin%20et%20al._This%20is%20How%20we%20Do%20it_Pitt%20Poster%20for%20CESF%202025.png', '  Sarode, Trupti and Gauvin, Nancy and Durham, Aliya and Caldwell, Keith  (2025) This is How we Do It: Lessons Learned from Three Branches of Community Engagement at Pitt.  In: 2025 Community Engaged Scholarship Forum, 2025-03-04, University of Pittsburgh.    (Unpublished)  ']}